Reasoning: The paper proposes a deep learning system for analyzing X-ray images for pneumonia and tuberculosis, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The system is fully automated and capable of understanding disease features without any manual feature extraction, which suggests the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions achieving state-of-the-art performance on public databases, which indicates the use of information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Finally, the system deals with medical images, which could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
